data.description: Your dream home awaits in the heart of Carrollwood! This captivating 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom NO HOA single-family pool home has undergone a complete transformation, leaving no stone unturned in its renovation. Perfectly blending modern aesthetics with thoughtful design, this property is an absolute gem. Brand new appliances, 20 minutes from Tampa International Airport, short drive to beaches, and theme parks.    Key Features:    Location, Location, Location: Nestled in the coveted Carrollwood area, this home offers a prime location with easy access to top-rated schools, shopping, and dining.    Complete Remodel: Every inch of this home has been meticulously remodeled, resulting in a fresh and modern interior that's sure to impress.    Open and Airy: The open-concept layout creates an inviting atmosphere with a seamless flow from the living room to the dining area. Vaulted ceilings and large windows flood the space with natural light.    Custom Kitchen: The heart of this home is its brand new kitchen, featuring brand-new stainless steel appliances, sleek quartz countertops, ample storage, and a spacious peninsula for culinary enthusiasts. It's perfect for entertaining or preparing family meals.    Elegant Bedrooms: The three bedrooms have been tastefully designed with comfort in mind. New flooring, fresh paint, and generous closet space ensure a cozy retreat for everyone.    Luxurious Bathrooms: Both bathrooms have been beautifully updated with modern fixtures, designer tile, and premium finishes for a spa-like experience.    Private Oasis: Step out to your screened lanai and inviting pool, surrounded by a lush backyard. Whether you're cooling off on a hot summer day or hosting a poolside barbecue, this outdoor space offers a serene escape.    2-Car Garage: The attached two-car garage provides convenience and extra storage space for your needs.    This meticulously renovated single-family pool home offers the perfect blend of style, comfort, and convenience. If you've been searching for the ideal family home or a serene retreat to enjoy Florida living, this property is an absolute must-see. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your new home. Schedule a showing today and experience the best of Carrollwood living!
